            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雍智科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6683:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6683\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6683-TW</a>)25日13:30股價上漲80元，報1180.0元，漲幅7.27%，成交215張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雍智科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6683:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6683\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6683-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為IC測試載板。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌5.17%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.58%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-37 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+39 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
